00:24.733 --> 00:27.655
Promise me that if you
ever feel suicidal again,

00:27.680 --> 00:28.872
you'll just come to me.

00:29.038 --> 00:31.213
The jury finds the defendants

00:31.946 --> 00:33.129
not liable.

00:33.154 --> 00:34.437
